snippet.title: Warframe - Nintendo Switch Reveal Trailer - TennoCon 2018
snippet.description:
The hit cooperative, sci-fi action game, Warframe, is coming to Nintendo Switch! 

They were called Tenno. Warriors of blade and gun – masters of the Warframe armor. Those that survived the Old War were left drifting among the ruins. Now they are needed once more. 

Learn more about Warframe: https://warframe.com/
